n太好了～～～～！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"event30-07-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"香澄","body":"總覺得！　樂音！\n就像是要一口氣衝上天花板一樣！\n我一邊唱著一邊起了雞皮疙瘩呢！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"event30-07-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"那種感覺我非常懂！\n不愧是音樂展演空間主辦的活動，\n深切感到對音響的堅持！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"event30-07-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"有咲","body":"的、的確……\n非常震撼……\n我的腳都在發抖了……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"event30-07-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"里美","body":"而且觀眾人數好多對吧！？\n我覺得我心臟都快要爆裂開來了！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"event30-07-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"但看起來沒那麼緊張喔？\n特別是小惠。\n感覺就是笑得很開心","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event30-07-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"多惠","body":"因為我真的很開心嘛！\n能在那個舞台上演奏，我真的好高興！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"event30-07-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"那種感覺完全傳達出來了喔。\n……啊，對了。\n原來如此，原來是這樣啊……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event30-07-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"有咲","body":"怎麼了嗎，麻里奈小姐？\n突然間好像領悟什麼道理……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"event30-07-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"我說聽了Popipa的演奏會開心，\n一定是因為你們五個人都很盡情享受音樂\n……我想是這樣～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event30-07-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"音樂果然……\n還是要樂在其中才行呢！\n多虧有你們我才能重新認知到這件事情","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event30-07-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"謝謝！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event30-07-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"香澄","body":"怎、怎麼這麼說！　該道謝的是我們！\n多虧有麻里奈小姐，\n才能在這麼厲害的地方表演LIVE！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"event30-07-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"……那個，之前有稍微提到對吧？\n我以前玩過樂團的事情","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event30-07-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"香澄","body":"啊，有！\n我好想聽喔！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"event30-07-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"雖然樂團早在很久以前就解散了，\n我們算是很認真以成為專業為目標。\n和Popipa一樣是五個人組成的女孩樂團","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event30-07-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"咦，原來是這樣啊……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"event30-07-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"所以說大家都很拼命努力，拼命在練習……\n有很多聽眾追隨著我們。\n也在各個音樂展演空間演奏過","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event30-07-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"只要呈現出很棒的演奏，一定會有人發掘我們……\n只要呈現出很棒的演奏，就絕對能邁向專業……\n大家都是這麼相信的……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event30-07-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"因為出名音樂家的訪談上都寫著\n如夢似幻般的故事，\n都說是在街頭LIVE被發掘……之類的？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event30-07-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"呵呵……\n現在回想起來，或許是因為年紀還小吧？\n總有一天我們也會爬上枝頭……我一直這麼想","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event30-07-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"香澄","body":"麻里奈小姐……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"event30-07-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"但是到頭來誰也沒發掘我們……\n也沒人理會我們……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event30-07-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"當時樂團也逐漸四散……\n再也沒人想要拿\n我們的LIVE宣傳單……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event30-07-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"但我現在就懂了，為什麼會變成那樣。\n因為演奏的人根本就不開心……\n這樣觀眾是不可能會高興的對吧？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event30-07-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,